  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced", 
    "date": "1998-10-08", 
    "text": "Homeowners' Emergency Mortgage Assistance Act - Directs the Secretary of Housing and Urban Development to establish a mortgage emergency assistance program for qualifying homeowners with National Housing Act-insured mortgages who are unable to temporarily meet their obligations due to financial hardship beyond their control. Requires homeowner repayment of such assistance and interest."
